      "content": "i was just looking at some photos of deep space tonight and i couldnt stop thinking about how everything is just... nothing. like, in a billion years none of this matters. not my mistakes, not my life, not anyone's. everything we do is just a temporary flicker in an empty void. it feels so pointless to even try anymore. why bother struggling through every day when the end result is just absolute zero?",
